{
  "title": "Creamy Brazilian Chicken Stew",
  "description": "This creamy stew is a traditional Brazilian dish featuring a rich garlic sauce and a sweet glaze, perfect for a sick day, and is halal-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Brazilian",
